long_description: IndexIQ Active ETF Trust - IQ Ultra Short Duration ETF is an exchange traded fund launched by New York Life Investment Management LLC. It is co-managed by IndexIQ Advisors LLC and NYL Investors LLC. The fund invests in fixed income markets across the globe. It invests directly and through other funds in fixed income securities including U.S. Government securities  like Treasury notes, obligations, repurchase agreements, agency securities, corporate bonds, instruments of non-U.S. issuers, asset-backed securities, mortgage-backed securities, commercial mortgage-backed securities, commercial paper, debentures, floating rate bonds, and convertible corporate bonds rated by BBB- or higher by S&P or Fitch or Baa3 or higher by Moodyâ€™s. The fund invests in securities with an average duration of 1 year or less. IndexIQ Active ETF Trust - IQ Ultra Short Duration ETF was formed on July 31, 2019 and is domiciled in the United States.
